==== Sample Configuration
	Sys Id : 8c49f4f14f110300e7cd4fe18110c79b

=== Detailed Description
This handler allows you to retrieve an incident from Service Now. It takes the input parameters and
then passes them in a REST call to Service Now to retrieve the incident.
